SELECT
    TOP 100 *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://synstg.blob.core.windows.net/syn-fs/delta/bronze/Product/',
        FORMAT = 'DELTA'

where ProductId<710
order by dateinserted desc;
